OL,3,C'The sums don't add up': Leaseholders
OL,4,Cshocked as bills go up 215%
OL,6,FITV Granada reporter Siham Ali spoke
OL,7,Fto residents on the estate about how
OL,8,Fthe sudden increase will affect their
OL,9,Flives.
OL,11,FAn elderly leaseholder whose monthly
OL,12,Fservice charge is set to increase by
OL,13,F215% says she feels "physically sick"
OL,14,Fat the thought of paying the
OL,15,F"unaffordable" fee.
OL,17,FThe residents on a housing estate,
OL,18,FCheshire, have seen their monthly
OL,19,Fpayments suddenly increase from
OL,20,Froughly #80 to more than #260.
