OL,3,C'The sums don't add up': Leaseholders
OL,4,Cshocked as bills go up 215%
OL,6,FShe said: "It's basically doubled in
OL,7,Fthe last twelve years from #40 to #84.
OL,8,FBut the letter I received three weeks
OL,9,Fago says it's increased to #265.50 a
OL,10,Fmonth."
OL,12,FNow, Gloria is unsure of where she'll
OL,13,Fget the money to pay the fees.
OL,15,FShe said: "It made me feel physically
OL,16,Fsick. Where am I going to get the
OL,17,Fmoney from? My pension has gone up
OL,18,F8.5%...the maintenance fee has gone up
OL,19,F215%.
OL,21,F"The sums just don't add up."
