OL,3,C'The sums don't add up': Leaseholders
OL,4,Cshocked as bills go up 215%
OL,6,FResidents including Gloria have
OL,7,Freported issues with mould and roof
OL,8,Fdamage to Realty, but say the repairs
OL,9,Fshould come at a fair and reasonable
OL,10,Fprice.
OL,12,FA few doors down from Gloria, Martin
OL,13,FKing has been unable to work due to
OL,14,Fhealth issues. He says the sharp
OL,15,Fincrease makes it impossible for him
OL,16,Fto afford living at the property.
OL,18,FHe said: "I've lived here for 24 years
OL,19,Fand I've always loved it here. It's a
OL,20,Fnice little community and we all help
OL,21,Feach other out.
