OL,6,F"But this has put a lot of stress and
OL,7,Fworry not just on myself but on other
OL,8,Fresidents. I just manage what I pay at
OL,9,Fthe moment, but to put it up to #265 a
OL,10,Fmonth... I just can't manage that.
OL,12,F"If they stick to their guns and
OL,13,Fthere's no leeway, I just don't know
OL,14,Fhow I'm going to budget for it."
